OL,3,CChris Kaba's family 'fight to get
OL,4,Cjustice' three years after police
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FThe family of Chris Kaba said they are
OL,8,Fexpecting news in the coming weeks on
OL,9,Fboth the inquest into his death and
OL,10,Fmisconduct proceedings involving the
OL,11,Fofficer who shot him.
OL,13,FMr Kaba, 24, was a member of one of
OL,14,FLondon's most violent street gangs and
OL,15,Fwas fatally shot after trying to ram
OL,16,Fhis way past police cars in Streatham,
OL,17,Fsouth-east London, in September 2022.
OL,19,FHis family marked the three-year
OL,20,Fanniversary of his death on September
OL,21,F5 with a private vigil.
