OL,3,CChris Kaba's family 'fight to get
OL,4,Cjustice' three years after police
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan police marksman who
OL,8,Fshot him, Martyn Blake, was cleared of
OL,9,Fmurder after an Old Bailey trial in
OL,10,FOctober last year.
OL,12,FHe is still due to face gross
OL,13,Fmisconduct proceedings over the
OL,14,Fshooting, a decision branded
OL,15,F"nonsensical" by officers' group the
OL,16,FMetropolitan Police Federation and
OL,17,Fopposed by force bosses.
