OL,3,CChris Kaba's family 'fight to get
OL,4,Cjustice' three years after police
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FBut watchdog the Independent Office
OL,8,Ffor Police Conduct ruled in April that
OL,9,Fhe should face a hearing, a decision
OL,10,Fwelcomed by Mr Kaba's family and the
OL,11,Fcharity Inquest.
OL,13,FA full inquest is due to be held into
OL,14,Fhis death on a date to be fixed.
OL,16,FIn a statement this week, issued
OL,17,Fthrough their solicitors Hickman and
OL,18,FRose, they said: "As they mark the
OL,19,Fthird anniversary of his death, the
OL,20,Ffamily of Chris Kaba continue in their
OL,21,Ffight to get justice for Chris.
OL,26,@zD@ROU
