OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,F"Those efforts did not end with the
OL,8,Facquittal of Martyn Blake last year.
OL,10,F"Blake is still to face gross
OL,11,Fmisconduct proceedings in which he
OL,12,Fmust account for his actions and, if
OL,13,Ffound to have breached his
OL,14,Fprofessional standards, should lose
OL,15,Fhis job.
OL,17,F"Chris' family also seek a full and
OL,18,Ffearless inquest into the wider
OL,19,Fcircumstances in which Chris was
OL,20,Fkilled.
