OL,3,CChris Kaba's family 'fight to get
OL,4,Cjustice' three years after police
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FThey did not know who was driving the
OL,8,Fcar at the time although it later
OL,9,Femerged Mr Kaba was a core member of
OL,10,Fone of London's most dangerous street
OL,11,Fgangs and was accused of being
OL,12,Finvolved in two shootings in the week
OL,13,Fbefore he died.
OL,15,FThe decision to charge Mr Blake with
OL,16,Fmurder sparked fury among firearms
OL,17,Fofficers, with dozens downing tools in
OL,18,Foutrage and the army being put on
OL,19,Fstandby in case needed to plug the gap.
